---
import ReactTowerDefenseApp from './ReactTowerDefenseApp';
import TdHud from './TdHud';
---

<div class="not-content w-full h-full">
	<div
		id="towerdefense-game-container"
		class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-2 border-gray-700 shadow-xl focus:outline-none relative bg-[#0d1117]"
		style="width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 16/9;"
		tabindex="0">
		<div id="towerdefense-game-inner" class="w-full h-full">
			<ReactTowerDefenseApp client:only="react" />
		</div>
		<div class="td-hud-mount">
			<TdHud client:only="react" />
		</div>
	</div>
	<p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2 text-center">
		Pick a build (<kbd>1</kbd>–<kbd>9</kbd>, <kbd>0</kbd>), click an empty
		tile to place. Click any existing tower to open its upgrade panel
		(Radar, Attack, Speed, Armor). Generators feed the global grid;
		batteries store surplus. Repair stations dispatch drones to fix damaged
		buildings. Brutes (purple) stop to chew nearby builds — runners and
		scouts speed past. Artillery hits anywhere on the map but fires slowly.
		Press <kbd>N</kbd>
		for a fresh map · <kbd>R</kbd> after game over.
	</p>
</div>

<style>
	#towerdefense-game-container {
		container-type: inline-size;
		touch-action: none;
		-webkit-user-select: none;
		user-select: none;
	}
	@container (max-width: 600px) {
		#towerdefense-game-container {
			aspect-ratio: 4/3;
		}
	}

	.td-hud-mount {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		pointer-events: none;
		z-index: 5;
		color: #f7fafc;
		font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
	}

	.td-hud-root {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
	}

	.td-hud-bar {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: stretch;
		padding: 8px 16px;
		background: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.9);
		border-bottom: 2px solid #374151;
		pointer-events: auto;
	}

	.td-hud-left {
		display: flex;
		gap: 24px;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.td-hud-right {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-end;
		gap: 8px;
	}

	.td-hud-stat {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		min-width: 60px;
	}

	.td-hud-stat-label {
		font-size: 11px;
		color: #a0aec0;
		letter-spacing: 0.04em;
	}

	.td-hud-stat-value {
		font-size: 20px;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1.1;
	}

	.td-hud-timer {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-end;
		gap: 8px;
	}

	.td-hud-skip-btn {
		padding: 4px 10px;
		font-family: inherit;
		font-size: 12px;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #fbd38d;
		background: #111827;
		border: 2px solid #fbd38d;
		border-radius: 4px;
		cursor: pointer;
		pointer-events: auto;
	}

	.td-hud-skip-btn:hover {
		background: #1f2937;
	}

	.td-hud-overlay {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 12px;
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
		pointer-events: auto;
		z-index: 10;
	}

	.td-hud-overlay-text {
		font-size: 36px;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.td-hud-restart-btn {
		padding: 14px 36px;
		font-family: inherit;
		font-size: 20px;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #fbd38d;
		background: #111827;
		border: 2px solid #fbd38d;
		border-radius: 6px;
		cursor: pointer;
	}

	.td-hud-restart-btn:hover {
		background: #1f2937;
	}

	.td-hud-overlay-hint {
		font-size: 11px;
		color: #a0aec0;
	}
</style>
